1280
01:22:01,137 --> 01:22:02,180
Kami aman di sini.

1281
01:22:02,347 --> 01:22:06,269
<i>Badai kilat di Orlando menyebabkan</i>
<i>ledakan mengerikan di DNC.</i>

1282
01:22:07,061 --> 01:22:09,939
<i>Tidak ada kabar resmi</i>
<i>tentang keberadaan Presiden...</i>

