Presiden Amerika Serikat.

1315
01:24:20,417 --> 01:24:21,752
Mereka datang.

1316
01:24:28,592 --> 01:24:29,427
Tembak.

1317
01:24:56,540 --> 01:24:59,294
Pikirmu hanya Presiden
yang bisa dilacak?

1318
01:25:08,179 --> 01:25:10,014
