<i>Butuh bantuan?</i>

1419
01:31:56,380 --> 01:31:57,590
<i>Salah pintu.</i>

1420
01:32:02,136 --> 01:32:03,221
<i>Kenapa kau di sini?</i>

1421
01:32:03,387 --> 01:32:05,724
<i>Sudah kubilang.</i>
<i>Aku tinggal di sini.</i>

1422
01:32:18,404 --> 01:32:21,574
<i>Waktu menjelang badai bumi,</i>
<i>satu menit, 40 detik.</i>

1423
01:32:31,460 --> 01:32:34,464
ANTARMUKA TERDETEKSI

1424
01:32:35,257 --> 01:32:36,883
<i>Mengunggah kode penutup.</i>

1425
01:32:54,069 --> 01:32:56,613
<i>Penutupan satelit dimulai.</i>

1426
01:32:59,701 --> 01:33:02,745
<i>Ketika siklus satelit terakhir berhenti,</i>
<i>kabari aku.</i>

1427
01:33:03,037 --> 01:33:05,832
<i>Aku akan mengulang seluruh sistem</i>
<i>secara manual.</i>

1428
01:33:05,999 --> 01:33:07,959
<i>- Itu akan membersihkan virusnya.</i>
<i>- Baik.</i>

1429
01:33:09,962 --> 01:33:11,005
DAYA MENYALA

1430
01:33:31,610 --> 01:33:32,945
<i>Lima lagi.</i>

1431
01:33:38,535 --> 01:33:39,536
<i>Tiga.</i>

1432
01:33:39,703 --> 01:33:41,204
<i>- Ayolah.</i>
<i>- Dua.</i>

1433
01:33:42,998 --> 01:33:43,874
<i>Dan satu.</i>

1434
01:33:46,627 --> 01:33:48,046
<i>Pengulangan manual diaktifkan.</i>

1435
01:34:03,812 --> 01:34:07,192
PERINGATAN BADAI BUMI

