<i>Kursi penonton terbaik.</i>

1446
01:35:08,217 --> 01:35:09,219
<i>Ute...</i>

1447
01:35:11,805 --> 01:35:13,557
<i>kau percaya akan doa di saat terakhir?</i>

1448
01:35:15,267 --> 01:35:17,769
<i>Ikuti aku. Kita harus ke satelit.</i>

1449
01:35:57,230 --> 01:35:58,231
<i>Aku memegangmu.</i>

1450
01:36:03,570 --> 01:36:06,991
<i>Kita harus sejauh mungkin</i>
<i>sebelum ledakan terakhir.</i>

1451
01:36:08,201 --> 01:36:09,327
<i>Melepaskan pengunci.</i>

1452
01:36:30,350 --> 01:36:33,437
PELEDAKAN DIRI SELESAI

1453
01:36:48,828 --> 01:36:52,375
<i>Tampaknya stasiun luar angkasa</i>
<i>sudah hancur.</i>

1454
01:36:52,542 --> 01:36:55,795
<i>Akhir yang tragis bagi dua pahlawan</i>
<i>yang masih di stasiun.</i>

1455
01:37:10,853 --> 01:37:12,480
Max, lihatlah.

1456
01:37:15,608 --> 01:37:16,943
