1457
01:37:18,152 --> 01:37:21,448
dan berkedip dalam pola Mayday.

1458
01:37:29,874 --> 01:37:32,085
Coba putar salah satu pesawat.

1459
01:37:42,179 --> 01:37:44,265
<i>Semoga ada yang melihat ini.</i>

1460
01:37:48,103 --> 01:37:49,605
<i>Semoga saja.</i>

1461
01:38:22,390 --> 01:38:24,810
<i>Hernandez, kau kurang ajar!</i>

1462
01:38:25,227 --> 01:38:26,479
